com.sociam.android.model

Class RecieveMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sociam.android.model.RecieveMessage

  • public class RecieveMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the model of messages from the server. It is used for plot message markers on the map. Each ReciveMessage holds a list of replymessages and a list of tags.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    yukki
